en.The game has 5 reels with reel 5 locked: The game has 5 reels with reel 5 locked in the main game.
en.The reel setup is 4-4-4-4-4 and a Convey: The reel setup is 4-4-4-4-4 and a Conveyor Belt beneath the bottom row. All reels are unlocked during the Tsunami Spins and Submerged Spins.
en.In main game the Wild symbols can land o: In main game the Wild symbols can land on any reel.
en.Partial and fully stacked character symb: Partial and fully stacked character symbols may land. Fully stacked character symbols convert into stacked Wild symbols.
en.When a submarine enters during any spin: When a submarine enters during any spin in main game or Tsunami Spins/ Submerged Spins, Titan Spin will be triggered. One of three Presidants may land in the submarine window and the multiplier of that Presidant will be applied to the base bet. If no Presidant lands, it is a no win.
en.Gets activated if there is a partially s: Gets activated if there is a partially stacked symbol on the same reel. It converts the partially stacked symbol to a fully stacked symbol.
en.Warning! 1 spin: Win or No Win!: Warning! 1 Spin: Win or No Win!
en.1 bottle will convert any random paying: 1 bottle will convert any random paying symbol on the same reel into Wild.
en.2 bottles —> First bottle will convert a: 2 bottles —> First bottle will convert any random paying symbol on the same reel into Wild and the second bottle will split that Wild symbol into two parts.
en.A half stacked Benzo Bear only exists in: A half stacked Benzo Bear only exists in main game and will convert 3-8 random symbols into Wild and/or Scatter.
en.A fully stacked Benzo Bear only exists i: A fully stacked Benzo Bear only exists in Submerged Spins and will convert all symbols below water surface into Wild.
en.Mr Split can only appear on reel 5 if it: Mr Split can only appear on reel 5 if it's unlocked and will split all symbols except Scatter from reel 1-5 on a row according to its size. It can appear half or fully stacked in the main game.
en.During Tsunami Spins and Submerged Spins: During Tsunami Spins and Submerged Spins, Mr Split appears as fully stacked symbol and will split all symbols that are below water surface.
en.Chainsaw will be active if Mr Split is p: Chainsaw will be active if Mr Split is present on unlocked reel 5. Chainsaw will add 1 more split to the already split positions on the same reel where it appears.
en.When appears during Tsunami Spins and/or: When appears during Tsunami Spins and/or Submerged Spins, it awards +2 spins per Rubber Duck.
en.Each Rubber Duck increases the level of: Each Rubber Duck increases the level of water by one row during Tsunami Spins.
en.If a Submarine filled with three Presida: If a Submarine filled with three Presidant enters on any spin, Titan Spin will be triggered. If an empty Submarine enters, it is a dead symbol.
en.Once Titan Spin is triggered, a spin is: Once Titan Spin is triggered, a spin is rewarded and one of the three Presidant will land on the reel. The multiplier of that Presidant will be applied to the base bet.
en.The three Presidants and their multiplie: The three Presidants and their multipliers are:
en.In main game the Scatter symbols can lan: In main game the Scatter symbols can land on any reel.
en.Landing one Scatter anywhere on reel 1-4: Landing one Scatter anywhere on reel 1-4 unlocks reel 5.
en.Landing 3/4/5 Scatter will trigger Tsuna: Landing 3/4/5 Scatter will trigger Tsunami Spins and will award 12/15/20 spins respectively.
en.All reels are active. It starts with bot: All reels are active. It starts with bottom 2 rows submerged under water.
en.When all 4 rows are covered by water, Ts: When all 4 rows are covered by water, Tsunami Spins are upgraded to Submerged Spins.
en.If Titan Spin is hit, Tsunami Spins will: If Titan Spin is hit, Tsunami Spins will complete first then Titan Spin will be triggered.
All 4 rows are covered by water level.
en.The max payout of the game is 57000 time: The max payout of the game is 57000 times the base bet.
en.When the total win exceeds this amount t: When the total win exceeds this amount the game round will end and 57000 times the base bet is awarded.
en.Land Of The Free is a video slot with f: Land Of The Free  is a video slot with following feature(s):
en.Titan Spin is termed as Idiot Spin for b: Titan Spin is termed as Idiot Spin for bonus buy.
en.At a cost of an extra 25%, the player is: At a cost of an extra 25%, the player is guaranteed a Scatter symbol on reel 1.
en.2 times more likely to trigger Tsunami S: 2 times more likely to trigger Tsunami Spins.
en.256 win ways by default (see pay table f: 256 win ways by default (see pay table for more info).
en.The theoretical return to the player for: The theoretical return to the player for xBet is -6%.
The theoretical return to the player for Tsunami Spins feature buy is -2%.
The theoretical return to the player for Submerged Spins feature buy is -3%.
The theoretical return to the player for Idiot Spin feature buy is -4%.
The theoretical return to the player for Lucky Draw feature buy is -5%.
en.If Titan Spin is hit, Submerged Spins wi: If Titan Spin is hit, Submerged Spins will complete first then Titan Spin will be triggered.
